title: Kylie’s seriously chic new bob
text:
Kylie Jenner debuts short and chic bob on social media news.com.au Kylie Jenner debuts short and chic bob on social media news.com.au Kylie Jenner debuts short and chic bob on social media. 
SHE’S known for her ever-changing and occasionally outrageous hairstyles. 
But Kylie Jenner’s new cut is surprisingly chic and understated. 
The 18-year-old debuted the short, dark bob on Instagram and Snapchat over the weekend. 
“Thanks for the dope blunt haircut,” she captioned a slow-motion video of herself on Instagram, which shows her hypnotically flicking the bob. Perfection 
But this understated new look probably won’t be around for long. 
Along with a pic of her once-green hair, she wrote: “Green has been my favourite so far. Def making a come back in the next few weeks.” Other Stories
